INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("359", "1", "2014-06-26 16:12:00", "2014-06-26 16:12:00", "[jumbotron heading=\"Thanks For Choosing Industrial Themes!\" tagline=\"We want you to get the most out of this theme. We\'ve rounded up every resource you could ever possibly need right here so you don\'t have to go searching through buried links and documents. Enjoy!\"]\n\n[clear]\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n[one_third]\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">[button type=\"link\" variation=\"btn-default\" link=\"http://industrialthemes.ticksy.com/faqs\" size=\"btn-lg\" target=\"blank\"][icons icon=\"help-circled\" color=\"#333333\" size=\"18\"] FAQs[/button]</p>\n[/one_third]\n\n[two_third_last]\nWe have provided detailed FAQs to help you with any question that might come up while using the theme. Nine out of ten times your question has already been answered in the FAQs.\n[/two_third_last]\n\n[clear]\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n[one_third]\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">[button type=\"link\" variation=\"btn-default\" link=\"http://www.industrialthemes.com/implicit/support/screencasts/\" size=\"btn-lg\" target=\"blank\"][icons icon=\"monitor\" color=\"#333333\" size=\"18\"] Screencasts[/button]</p>\n[/one_third]\n\n[two_third_last]\nSometimes words just don\'t do it. That\'s why we\'ve taken the extra time to create narrated Screencasts to visually explain the ins and outs of the most common functions of setting up this theme.\n[/two_third_last]\n\n[clear]\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n[one_third]\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">[button type=\"link\" variation=\"btn-default\" link=\"http://www.industrialthemes.com/implicit/support/documentation\" size=\"btn-lg\" target=\"blank\"][icons icon=\"doc\" color=\"#333333\" size=\"18\"] Documentation[/button]</p>\n[/one_third]\n\n[two_third_last]\nWhat good is a product without a user manual? This theme has been extensively documented to help you get setup as quickly as possible. Go ahead, have a read. It\'s good for you!\n[/two_third_last]\n\n[clear]\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n[one_third]\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">[button type=\"link\" link=\"http://industrialthemes.ticksy.com\" size=\"btn-lg\" variation=\"btn-danger\" target=\"blank\"][icons icon=\"comments\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" size=\"18\"] Support Center[/button]</p>\n[/one_third]\n\n[two_third_last]\nStuck? Can\'t find the answer in the documentation, FAQs, or screencasts? No problem, check out our handy support center. Feel free to post a question if you can\'t find the solution.\n[/two_third_last]\n\n[clear]\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n[one_third]\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">[button type=\"link\" variation=\"btn-default\" link=\"http://www.industrialthemes.com/implicit/support/credits\" size=\"btn-lg\" target=\"blank\"][icons icon=\"cc\" color=\"#333333\" size=\"18\"] Credits[/button]</p>\n[/one_third]\n\n[two_third_last]\nGiving credit where credit is due. Any external assets used by this theme, such as fonts, images, and code, are documented on our credits page.\n[/two_third_last]\n\n[clear]\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n[one_third]\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">[button type=\"link\" variation=\"btn-default\" link=\"http://themeforest.net/user/IndustrialThemes\" size=\"btn-lg\" target=\"blank\"][icons icon=\"leaf\" color=\"#333333\" size=\"18\"] ThemeForest[/button]</p>\n[/one_third]\n\n[two_third_last]\nLooking for us on ThemeForest? Click the button to go directly to our profile page in the popular theme marketplace. Of course, you\'ve probably already been there seeing as how that\'s where you purchased this theme!\n[/two_third_last]\n\n[clear]\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n[one_third]\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">[button type=\"link\" variation=\"btn-default\" link=\"http://www.industrialthemes.com\" size=\"btn-large\" target=\"blank\"][icons icon=\"globe\" color=\"#333333\" size=\"18\"] Our Website[/button]</p>\n[/one_third]\n\n[two_third_last]\nThis is where we live on the old \'net. Click below to visit the home of IndustrialThemes, LLC. and see our portfolio and information about how to get in contact with us.\n[/two_third_last]\n\n[clear]\n\n[/jumbotron]", "Support", "", "publish", "open", "open", "", "support", "", "", "2014-06-26 16:12:00", "2014-06-26 16:12:00", "", "0", "http://www.industrialthemes.com/implicit/?page_id=359", "0", "page", "", "0");
