/li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/cocktails/5309919\">Cocktails</a> regular license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/beautiful-young-woman-with-a-skateboard/6802756\">Beautiful young woman with a skateboard</a> regular license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/luxury-sail-boat/5255221\">Luxury sail boat</a> regular license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/young-couple-with-umbrella/588966\">Young Couple With Umbrella</a> regular license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/young-couple/2674955\">Young couple</a> regular license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/hipster-young-stylish-man/4615765\">hipster young stylish man</a> regular license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/beautiful-girl/4046886\">Beautiful girl</a> regular license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/beautiful-young-girl-with-longboard-standing-on-the-tennis-court/7966607\">Beautiful young girl with longboard standing on the tennis court</a> regular license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://photodune.net/item/man-in-suit/6285901\">man in suit</a> regular license</li>\n</ul>\n[/lists]\n[/tab]\n[tab title=\"CODE\"]\nAll external code components and third-party code assets used in the theme are licensed appropriately and listed below:\n\n[lists style=\"check\" color=\"#000000\"]\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://twitter.github.io/bootstrap/index.html\">Boostrap</a> license: Apache License v2.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://users.tpg.com.au/j_birch/plugins/superfish/\">Superfish</a> license: MIT and GPL licenses</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.smoothdivscroll.com/\">SmoothDivScroll</a> license: GPL license</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://benalman.com/projects/jquery-resize-plugin/\">resize event</a> license: MIT and GPL licenses</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/davatron5000/FitVids.js\">Fitvids</a> license: <a href=\"http://www.wtfpl.net/\">WTFPL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.newmediacampaigns.com/page/jquery-flickr-plug